## TOP 10 MOST TARGETED BRANDS

1. **Credential Phishing** (130 attacks) - Generic email theft
2. **Amazon** (104 attacks) - E-commerce giant
3. **Sumitomo Mitsui Card** (81 attacks) - Major credit card
4. **AEON** (67 attacks) - Retail/department store
