## CRITICAL GAPS IN DEFENSES

ğŸ”´ **Email Authentication:** Most brands lack proper DMARC implementation  
ğŸ”´ **Consumer Awareness:** Low public knowledge of phishing tactics  
ğŸ”´ **Brand Monitoring:** Insufficient domain/web monitoring  
ğŸ”´ **Threat Sharing:** No coordinated intelligence sharing  
ğŸ”´ **Law Enforcement:** No coordinated investigation underway  

**Result:** Campaign operates successfully for 21 months without disruption

