## RECOMMENDATIONS

### Short-Term (0-3 Months)
- Deploy defensive infrastructure (DMARC, brand monitoring)
- Launch coordinated consumer awareness campaign
- Initiate law enforcement investigation
- Establish industry threat-sharing consortium

### Medium-Term (3-12 Months)
- Advance to passwordless authentication where possible
- Deploy AI-powered phishing detection systems
- Coordinate domain takedown operations
- Implement zero-trust security architectures

### Long-Term (12+ Months)
- Establish permanent cybercrime coordination framework
- Integrate threat intelligence across all sectors
- Develop national digital literacy programs
- Create comprehensive victim support systems

